Package: McDisCov
Title: Outcome-linked Microbiome Discovery via Compositional lOgit-normal Modeling under Varying Support
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jiahao", "Wang", email = "10225000478@stu.ecnu.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Identify taxa whose absolute and relative abundances are associated with covariates. McDisCoV unifies absolute and relative abundance inference under a compositional logit-normal model framework.
